C21F917B", "keywords_fra": "G\u00e9omatique,Donn\u00e9es g\u00e9ographiques,Photographie,Photographie a\u00e9rienne,Imagerie et carte de base,Bdpc,Photo a\u00e9rienne,Points d-appui au sol,Snrc 95e13", "title": "Ground Control Database, Canada - N61d56mW127d46m_4", "department_number": "115"}
{"data_series_issue_identification_fra": "1.0", "catalog_type": "Geo Data | G\\u00e9o", "title_fra": "CanImage - Landsat 7 Orthoimages of Canada, 1:50 000 - 094D07", "keywords": "Canimage-094d07-1.0,Earth science,Visible imagery,Visible radiance,National imagery,British columbia,Asitka river,094d07", "data_series_issue_identification": "1.0", "ready_to_publish": "0", "digital_object_identifier": "", "subject": "", "data_series_name_fra": "CanImage - Landsat 7 Orthoimages of Canada, 1:50 000", "spatial_representation_type": "Image Digital | Image num\u00e9rique", "maintenance_and_update_frequency": "Not Planned | Non planifi\u00e9", "author": "Natural Resources Canada | Ressources naturelles Canada", "author_email": "geoginfo@NRCan.gc.ca", "geographic_region": "", "notes_fra": "Le produit CanImage est une image matricielle contenant de l'information provenant des ortho-images Landsat 7 r\u00e9\u00e9chantillonn\u00e9es et d\u00e9coup\u00e9es selon le Syst\u00e8me national de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence cartographique (SNRC) \u00e0 l'\u00e9chelle de 1/50 000 dans la projection UTM. Ce produit est distribu\u00e9 par fichier dans le format GeoTIFF. La r\u00e9solution de ce produit est de 15 m\u00e8tres. Les ortho-images Landsat 7 contiennent 8 bandes spectrales. Pour la cr\u00e9ation du produit CanImage, les bandes 3 (rouge), 2 (verte) et 1 (verte-bleue) ont \u00e9t\u00e9 retenues. Ces bandes sont repr\u00e9sent\u00e9es par les couleurs rouge (bande 3), verte (bande 2) et bleue (bande 1). Un rehaussement lin\u00e9aire est effectu\u00e9 sur chacune des 3 bandes spectrales afin d'am\u00e9liorer le contraste des donn\u00e9es. Le d\u00e9coupage du produit selon le SNRC dans la projection UTM g\u00e9n\u00e8re un chevauchement entre les fichiers CanImage adjacents.", "id": "00084379-2cf6-44a8-91d6-aa8c022fca37", "presentation_form": "Image Digital | Image num\u00e9rique", "spatial": "{\"type\": \"Polygon\", \"coordinates\": [[[-127, 56.25], [-127, 56.5], [-126.5, 56.5], [-126.5, 56.25], [-127, 56.25]]]}", "license_id": "", "resources": [{"url": "http://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/canimage/50k/094/d/canimage_094d07_tif.zip", "language": "no language | aucune langue", "format": "GeoTIF"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/canimage/50k/094/d/canimage_094d07_tif.zip", "language": "no language | aucune langue", "format": "GeoTIF"}], "browse_graphic_url": "", "topic_category": "Imagery Base Maps Earth Cover  Imagerie carte de base couverture terrestre", "tags": [], "endpoint_url_fra": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/fr/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "date_published": "2010-11-02", "time_period_coverage_start": "2002-07-07", "data_series_name": "CanImage - Ortho-images Landsat 7 du Canada, 1/50 000", "endpoint_url": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/en/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "time_period_coverage_end": "2002-07-07", "notes": "CanImage is a raster image containing information from Landsat 7 orthoimages that have been resampled and based on the National Topographic System (NTS) at the 1:50 000 scale in the UTM projection. The product is distributed in files in GeoTIFF format. The resolution of this product is 15 metres. The Landsat 7 ortho images contain 8 spectral bands. For the creation of the CanImage product, the following bands were retained: band 3 (red), 2 (green) and 1 (green-blue). These bands are displayed using the colors: red (band 3), green (band 2) and blue (band 1). A linear stretching is done on each of the 3 band in order to increase the contrast. The clipping of the product according to the NTS in the UTM projection generate an overlap between the adjacent CanImage data sets.", "owner_org": "9391E0A2-9717-4755-B548-4499C21F917B", "keywords_fra": "Canimage-094d07-1.0,Sciences de la terre,Imagerie dans le visible,Radiance visible,Imagerie nationale,Colombie-britanique,Asitka river,094d07", "title": "CanImage - Ortho-images Landsat 7 du Canada, 1/50 000 - 094D07", "department_number": "115"}
